OL,3,CVehicle repair company fined after car
OL,4,Cfell on worker who was praying
OL,6,FA vehicle repair company has been
OL,7,Ffined after a worker was crushed by a
OL,8,Fcar which fell onto him from a vehicle
OL,9,Flift as he prayed.
OL,11,FMr Hamad, 56, was working as a
OL,12,Fmechanic in Liverpool, when the car,
OL,13,Fwhich had been raised on a two-post
OL,14,Flift came crashing to the ground in
OL,15,FNovember 2022.
