OL,3,CVehicle repair company fined after car
OL,4,Cfell on worker who was praying
OL,6,FAn investigation showed that neither
OL,7,Fof the swivel arms on one of the
OL,8,Flifting columns was locked into
OL,9,Fposition, at the Car Spa & Tyres Ltd.
OL,10,Fon Marvin Street and, as Mr Hamad took
OL,11,Fa break to pray, the car fell from the
OL,12,Flift, crushing him beneath and causing
OL,13,Fmultiple serious fractures.
OL,15,FHe was rushed to Aintree Hospital,
OL,16,Fwhere he was treated for a broken leg,
OL,17,Fthree broken bones in his spine, five
OL,18,Fbroken ribs and a broken pelvis,
OL,19,Fspending four months in hospital
OL,20,Fbecause of his injuries.
