OL,3,CVehicle repair company fined after car
OL,4,Cfell on worker who was praying
OL,6,FThe Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,7,Fsays that almost two years later, he
OL,8,Fhas been left highly dependent upon
OL,9,Fhis wife, and others, to carry out
OL,10,Feven simple daily tasks, and it is
OL,11,Funlikely he will be able to work again.
OL,13,FAn investigation by HSE found that Car
OL,14,FSpa & Tyres Ltd, had failed to put in
OL,15,Fplace a safe system of work, or to
OL,16,Fsufficiently train their staff, in the
OL,17,Fproper, and safe operation of the
OL,18,Flifting equipment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
