OL,3,CVehicle repair company fined after car
OL,4,Cfell on worker who was praying
OL,6,FThe company, based in the Kensington
OL,7,Farea of Liverpool, were convicted of
OL,8,Fbreaching regulation 2(1) of the
OL,9,FHealth and Safety at Work Act 1974 and
OL,10,Fwas fined #40,000 and ordered to pay
OL,11,F#20,000 in costs at Liverpool
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court.
OL,14,FAfter the hearing, HSE inspector David
OL,15,FBellis said: "This was a very serious
OL,16,Fincident, and it is fortunate nobody
OL,17,Fwas killed as a result.
