OL,6,F"If Mr Hamad had been suitably trained
OL,7,Fin the use of the two-post lift, the
OL,8,Fcompany had a suitable system of work
OL,9,Fin place and the swivel arms had been
OL,10,Fpositioned correctly and locked into
OL,11,Fplace this incident would have been
OL,12,Favoided.
OL,14,F"The HSE take all accidents seriously,
OL,15,Fespecially those that could have been
OL,16,Feasily prevented, and will not
OL,17,Fhesitate to prosecute, whenever it is
OL,18,Fappropriate."
